Package KI305.Symanyshyn.Lab2

Class ClimberEquipment

java.lang.Object
KI305.Symanyshyn.Lab2.ClimberEquipment
public class ClimberEquipment extends Object
Represents a set of climbing equipment including a rope, harness, and helmet. Provides various methods to interact with and manipulate the equipment.
